From BettyRats.com:

&quot;Betty Rats, a roots revival band from Nashville, TN, plays an off-kilter style of electric folk that contains elements of jug band and gypsy music. They embrace a back-to-basics approach to recording and performing live that features stripped-down instrumentation and production techniques. This method allows them to incorporate aspects of improvisation and spontaneous expression into most every performance, either live or recorded.

