Betty Rats has played over 60 shows in the past two years including two tours of the East Coast and the Midwest. They recorded and released an eight-song self-titled EP in June of 2007. And their debut full length Squeaks Tall Reeds was released by For the Philistine Records on September 27th 2008.&quot;
